These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, tiparillo, siglo, ritmeester
4 different pets are kept: pony, mouse, guinea-pig, bird
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, lily, daffodil, sunflower
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, superhero, western
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, april, january, november
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, ice-hockey, lacrosse, soccer
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, polish, brazilian, indian
 1. the cain-smoker is the person watching action movies##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 4. the person who growslily is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growslily is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 6. the mexican is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the indian is the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the polish is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
11. the person who's sport is biathlon is the tiparillo-smoker##1
12. the polish is the person who's birthday is in january##1
13. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
14. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the ritmeester-smoker##1
15. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who growsdaffodil##1
16. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
17. the siglo-smoker is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4      |
| Cigar      | cain       | ritmeester      | siglo       | tiparillo    |
| Pet         | pony    | bird    | mouse      | guinea-pig    |
| Flower           | sunflower | marigold       | daffodil | lily     |
| Movie-Genre   | action         | superhero  | western      | comedy     |
| Birthday   | april          | november     | january       | march |
| Sport         | lacrosse       | ice-hockey | soccer       | biathlon   |
| Nationality     | indian     | brazilian  | polish         | mexican   |

