House: cape-cod, victorian, modern, futuristic
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, dannemann, cain, dunhill
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, april, october
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, dancer, coach, librarian
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, horse, rabbit
City: liverpool, edinburgh, venice, new-york
 1. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 2. the dancer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 3. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the victorian house##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is the dannemann-smoker##1
 6. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the modern house##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 8. the cain-smoker is the cape-cod house##1
 9. the security-guard is on the left of the librarian##1
10. the victorian house is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
11. the owner of the horse is on the right of the game-smoker##1
12. the librarian is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
13. the victorian house is on the far right##1
14. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
15. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
16. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
17. the librarian is on the right of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3      |      4      |
