.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, green, lilac, light-blue
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, indonesian, american, italian
4 different games are played: snooker, backgammon, billiard, canasta
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, epic, horror, time-travel
House: tower, craftsman, victorian, townhouse
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, lizard, rat
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, lemonade, cola, juice
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 2. the person who likes green is on the right of the american##1
 3. the tower house is the person who likes green##1
 4. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the brazilian##1
 5. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the rat is the person watching epic movies##1
11. the person playing backgammon is the person who likes blood-red##1
12. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
13. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
14. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
15. the indonesian is the townhouse house##1
16. the person playing canasta is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
17. the person drinking cola is on the left of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |     3     |      4      |
| Color          | lilac          | light-blue        | green      | blood-red      |
| Nationality         | italian       | american       | brazilian    | indonesian |
